<sect1 id="config.post.permitanyone">
	<title>
	case study: anyone can post.
	</title>

<para>
<screen>
post_restrictions = permit_anyone
</screen>
$post_restrictions parameter controls who can post to this ML.
To set this as "permit_anyone", anybody can post.
</para>

<para>
By default, 
<screen>
post_restrictions	=	reject_system_special_accounts
				permit_member_maps
				reject
</screen>
"reject_system_special_accounts" denys post if
From: looks like system accounts e.g. root, postmaster.
</para>

</sect1>
